invalid type: string "Scalability\nNewdocumentscanbeaddedwithoutretrainingthelanguagemodel.\nTheseadvantagesmakeRAGhighlyeffectiveforbusinessapplications.\nChallenges of RAG\nDespiteitsbenefits,RAGalsofaceschallenges.\nPoor Chunking\nImproperchunksizesmayreduceretrievalquality.\nWeak Embeddings\nLow-qualityembeddingscanretrieveirrelevantcontent.\nRetrieval Errors\nb7}\nSeveralsentences\n\u{f0b7}\n